headline: American Electric Power Company, Inc. (AEP) in Focus as Morgan Stanley Reassesses Regulated Utilities
summary: American Electric Power Company, Inc. (NASDAQ:AEP) is included among Dividend Contenders List: Top 20 Stocks. On January 21, Morgan Stanley raised its price target on American Electric Power Company, Inc. (NASDAQ:AEP) to $125 from $120. It maintained an Overweight rating on the stock.
